dogs.name: Yanmar
dogs.description:
Gold-Sierra Yanmar was imported directly from Gold-Sierra Kennel in Hungary in the fall of 2018.  This boy has consistently cloned himself time and time again.  With a super small stature, yet having a huge head, massive bone and lots of substance, he is an ideal French Bulldog specimen.  He weighs 20-22lbs and is standard colors only, but does carry pied.  Yanmar is also health tested clear of CMR1, PRA cord1, DM, HUU and JHC.  He will be closed to the public after July 9th of 2023 when he turns 5 years old.



Yanmar is retired to the public but will still be used in house here and there

dogs.name: Party Monster
dogs.description:
Texas Top Notch Party Monster was produced right here back in June of 2018.  He is our smallest stud weighing a whopping 17-18 lbs.  Party Monster is super small, compact and has a beautiful headpiece.  He is also probably our quietest and most laid back dog.  Party Monster has produced many offspring that have his beautiful look while staying small, including his daughter, Rudolph, we have here.  He is standard colors but does carry a copy of cocoa.  Party Monster is health tested clear of CMR1, PRA-cord1, DM, HUU, JHC and Cystinuria 3. This boy is open for stud and we have the ability to ship same day or overnight.



Stud Fee: $2000 (Party Monster will be closing to the public June 21, 2023)

dogs.name: Odyn
dogs.description:
Texas Top Notch Odyn the Great was produced right here back in March of 2020.  This guy is out of our amazing Yanmar and is a prime example of the quality Yanmar produces.  He is 1/2 brother to Yuki , Yenko, Yuli and Yakka. Odyn is built like a box and has an amazing head with a full rope, ridiculous bone and lots of substance on his small, compact frame.  He is a tad heavier than his daddy but almost identical in height and structure.  This guy looks like a little teddy bear and is the sweetest dog.  Odyn is health tested clear of  JHC, DM, HUU, PRA-Cord1, CMR1 and Cystinuria 3.  He is standard colors but carries both cream and pied.  He is the sire to our beautiful girl, Neva that can be seen on the females page.



Stud Fee: $2500
